    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "makes sense. i'm seeing a few tiny cracks or little gaps appearing in some of the old seams near the floor/baseboard area as i'm prepping. is that just normal settling or is there something wrong with how the previous guy did it? how do i patch those small holes so they don't keep coming back?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
